      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="cta-content">
          <h2>See Trinity Garden in Person</h2>
          <p>
            Photos can only tell part of the story. We invite you to schedule a
            personal tour to experience the warmth, care, and community that
            make Trinity Garden special.
          </p>
          <div class="cta-buttons">
